ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔覺有呢d片睇係好值得自豪既事</blockquote><br />\n撚狗片有咩所謂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講返個Post講嘅台灣，其實唔止槍戰，捉人揸快車或者唔守交通規矩個啲其實都幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，依個香港應該唔少喇下嘛"},{"pid":"c1ca7f1c908062eb68a2506dbe0b4cc7b5d265d5","tid":503431,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n<br />\n好睇"},{"pid":"a5080caa6b93ef75b009466c2922ca99dbf8de81","tid":503431,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:05:09.000Z","msg":"香港警察乜柒風險都冇但係人工冠絕全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4f38e868ba1b822204a18cf1c74ff3ba9d3b0a","tid":503431,"uid":99175,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你想香港有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到香港無拍片就無人犯法咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港有幾可出槍追人呀 人口咁密集<br />\n仲有香港以人口密度計 犯罪率係好少<br />\n自然唔會有呢d鏡頭出現</blockquote><br />\n有無見過瑞士 芬蘭呢類北歐少罪案國家<br />\n會放呢類警匪追逐戰睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔覺有呢d片睇係好值得自豪既事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 主要國家故意殺人案－犯罪率\t\t   單位：件/十萬人口<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n國  別  2008年 2009年 2010年 2011年 2012年 2013年 2014年 2015年<br />\n中華民國\t0.87\t0.85\t0.76\t0.63\t0.73\t0.66\t0.55\t<span style=\"color: red;\">0.61</span><br />\n瑞　　典\t2.27\t2.47\t3.51\t2.42\t2.48\t3.00\t3.27\t<span style=\"color: red;\">3.11</span><br />\n芬　　蘭\t3.01\t2.58\t2.50\t2.49